{"data":[{"name":"114:1","price":"\"Ka ce \"Ina nẽman tsari ga Ubangijin mutãne.\"","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"\"Mamallakin mutane.\"","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"\"Abin bautãwar mutãne.\"","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"\"Daga sharrin mai sanya wasuwãsi, mai ɓoyewa.\"*","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Shaiɗan yakan ɓõye idan ya ji an ambaci sunan Allah, dõmin haka aka yi masa suna mai ɓõyewa, wãto bã ya zuwa wurin da ake karatu da wa'azi, kamar yadda bã ya zama cikin zũciyar mutum mai ibãda da gaskiya. Ibãda ta gaskiya ita ce wadda aka yi ta kamar yadda Allah Ya ce a yi ta. Banda ibãdar bidi'a, ba ta korar Shaiɗan. Kuma da sharaɗin a yi ibãdar da kyakkyawar niyya, dõmin aikin da bãbu niyya mai kyãwu game da shi ɓãtacce ne.","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"\"Wanda ke sanya wasuwãsi a cikin ƙirãzan mutane.\"","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"\"Daga aljannu da mutane.\"","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}}],"chapter":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas","Chapter An-Nas","Nas","Surah Nas","Chapter Nas","An Nas","Surah An Nas","Chapter An Nas","Surah 114","Chapter 114","Mankind","الناس"],"version":{"key":"hausa_gummi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ha","version":"1.2.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Hausa language - Abu Bakr Jomy","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Hausa by Abu Bakr Mahmoud Jomy. Corrected by supervision of Rowwad Translation Center. The original translation is available for suggestions, continuous evaluation and development."}}